Package org.apache.wayang.core.types

Class DataSetType<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.wayang.core.types.DataSetType<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class DataSetType<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A data set is an abstraction of the Wayang programming model. Although never directly materialized, a data set keeps track of type and structure of data units being passed between operators.
    See Also:
